This paper is primarily focused on the stability and optimization of GANs, which is a topic that falls under the umbrella of machine learning. The paper also discusses the use of optimal transport, which is a topic that falls under the category of information theory (cs.IT). The paper's focus on stability and optimization also suggests that it could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
